<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.6.1">
<l>tīrppārai yāmiṉi yeṅṅaṉa nāṭutu maṉṉaimī</l>
<l>rōrppāliv voṇṇuta luṟṟanaṉ ṉōyitu tēṟiṉōm</l>
<l>pōrppāku tāṉcey taṉṟaivarai velvitta māyappōrt</l>
<l>tērppāka ṉārkkivaḷ cintai tuḻāytticaik kiṉṟatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A physian now, how will we seek [him], mothers?</l>
<l>By examination we understood this [is] the good pain suffered by this [girl with] bright forehead.</l>
<l>Her mind, stirred, subsides to him who drives the chariot of miraculous</l>
<l>warfare that brought victory to the Five that day, he himself acting as covering.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
